束前三节。 希尔德独取 6 分，哈利伯顿和琼斯各打 3 分成功，他们率队以 12-2 的反击波开始第四节，国王队以 95-88 反超。米尔斯三分回应，哈利伯顿连得 4 分，米切尔跳投命中，国王队以 103-93 领先 10 分。约翰逊连追 4 分迫近，梅图发力还击 5 分稳住局势。最后时刻篮网队进攻失准，他们无力回天以 101-112 落败。 篮网队首发阵容：哈登、欧文、米尔斯、爱德华兹、克拉克斯顿 国王队首发阵容：哈利伯顿、米切尔、巴恩斯、哈克利斯、霍姆斯唉…篮网不敌国王遭遇 6 连败 哈登仅 4 分欧文 15 中 5"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c95fe8bf8587fe3813ce199b8b036494_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "39 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/514553262"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iy4HGnfutt4d5EAMaCDc2NjI2NjMwIM/87I8GMAA4L0Abcgk1MTQ1NTMyNjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1643926028.4106333", "card_id": "Q_514371834", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 63}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "普通人如何迅速制服泰森一样的敌人？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "可以用器械，可以偷袭，可以致命攻击"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a944de8d567e8c03bc573c7ebc28a394_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/514371834"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iy4HGnfutt4d5EAMaCDc2NTg2MjczIN6n5Y8GMAU4WEAccgk1MTQzNzE4MzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1643926028.41098", "card_id": "Q_510475478", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 103}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "高三，支撑你们的是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-5b7e86c9c22d4d90ae0a56793b1a3274_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "17 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/510475478"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iy4HGnfutt4d5EAMaCDc1NzIwNTg2IKzN5I4GMAE42QFAHXIJNTEwNDc1NDc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1643926028.41